<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=101405977621265></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f101405977621265><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=8&mid=101405977621265>RE: General Questions for a 10th level druid</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=8&mid=101405977621265#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=133423><span id=Scholar>darkparable</span></a>, <span id=Scholar>Scholar</span><br><span id=notbold>23 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Feb 18th 2:16 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>First I just wanted to thank all of you (SemiMaster, Mistress Ancarett, Sdenchfi, and Lord Chking). I have only had the game for one month and it means a lot to be able to get this amount of expertise...so thanks for making my life easier.<br><br>Second...what a difference a week makes...I stumbled onto some very nice equipment deals:<br><br>I got the split paw gloves, a fine steel scimitar and I believe its called an Iskar stave (magic 1h blunt w/ low delay) fairly quickly. This diminished my income to 2pp. I thought geez I'm broke so I went out hunting and foraging like mad. In six hours I was back up to 45pp (I was amazed--again right place right time)<br><br>I just killed an orc centurion this morning and had a weird thing happen...it makes me wonder if some high level person had dumped equipment on the orc--if that's possible (if it is I might do that when I get higher level). I looted off one orc: cloth pants, CB belt, bronze spear, bronze short spear, and shiny brass halbred...I'm not even sure what to sell these for..but it's been a fun couple of days.<br><br>Thank you again for the strategies and the input.<br><br>Averill<br>Lvl 11 Druid<br>Morell-Thule<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Feb 18 14:20:49 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
